                                     {
                                         "text":  "<p><h3>Europe: Banu Qasi</h3>At the height of their power, between <htdate0> and <htdate1>, the Banu Qasi controlled the area highlighted in green in the image in this section",
                                         "source":  [
                                                        {
                                                            "type":  1,
                                                            "uuid":  "b43eff03-c370-4692-875a-2455e2c99d03",
                                                            "text":  "Juste, Alberto C.",
                                                            "page":  "pp. 29",
                                                            "date_time":  {
                                                                              "type":  "gregory",
                                                                              "year":  "1980",
                                                                              "month":  "",
                                                                              "day":  ""
                                                                          }
                                                        }
                                                    ],
                                         "date_time":  null,
                                         "isTable":  false,
                                         "imgdesc":  "",
                                         "format":  "html",
                                         "PostMention":  "."
                                     },
                                     {
                                         "text":  "The unification of Spain into a single political entity is relatively recent, taking place in <htdate0>. This unification contributed to Spain’s rich cultural and genetic diversity",
                                         "source":  [
                                                        {
                                                            "type":  1,
                                                            "uuid":  "732ffe6d-b8a9-42af-b070-16c18c82dbce",
                                                            "text":  "O'Callaghan, J. F. et al.",
                                                            "page":  "",
                                                            "date_time":  {
                                                                              "type":  "gregory",
                                                                              "year":  "",
                                                                              "month":  "",
                                                                              "day":  ""
                                                                          }
                                                        },
                                                        {
                                                            "type":  1,
                                                            "uuid":  "08ac929b-a863-4a22-b7ed-ca86966b7b10",
                                                            "text":  "Cartwright, M.",
                                                            "page":  "Reconquista",
                                                            "date_time":  {
                                                                              "type":  "gregory",
                                                                              "year":  "2018",
                                                                              "month":  "10",
