                                                                          }
                                                        }
                                                    ],
                                         "date_time":  null,
                                         "isTable":  false,
                                         "imgdesc":  "",
                                         "format":  "html",
                                         "PostMention":  "."
                                     },
                                     {
                                         "text":  "Recently, some research and discussions in historical forums have suggested possible connections between the Banu Qasi and later monarchs in the Iberian Peninsula, or even with the prophet Muhammad. However, no primary sources have yet been identified to support these hypotheses",
